WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:02.209
No, I didn't tell him.

2
00:00:02.209 --> 00:00:03.850
Why not?

3
00:00:03.850 --> 00:00:09.439
I don't want him to worry about me.

4
00:00:09.439 --> 00:00:14.439
If you were my wife, I wouldn't be happy if you kept it from me.

5
00:00:14.439 --> 00:00:44.060
The bleeding has stopped and the wound is dressed.

6
00:00:44.060 --> 00:00:47.060
I'm going back to my room to clean up myself.

7
00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:55.049
Jenny, I'm a little hungry.

8
00:00:55.049 --> 00:00:57.049
Want to grab a snack together?

9
00:00:57.049 --> 00:00:59.049
Mr. Miller, I can move my right hand. Let me do it myself.

10
00:00:59.049 --> 00:01:09.480
Don't get me wrong. I just don't want to owe anyone anything.

11
00:01:09.480 --> 00:01:12.480
Aren't you hungry, Mr. Miller? Why aren't you eating?

12
00:01:12.480 --> 00:01:13.480
The hunger went away.

13
00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:18.780
You're not doing this just for me, are you?

14
00:01:18.780 --> 00:01:20.780
Aren't you afraid your husband will get jealous?

15
00:01:20.780 --> 00:01:24.030
That's exactly why I asked.

16
00:01:24.030 --> 00:01:27.159
But, aren't you in deep love with your husband?

17
00:01:27.159 --> 00:01:29.260
Yeah, I love him very much.

18
00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:38.530
I'm off. You better sleep now.

19
00:01:38.530 --> 00:01:43.530
Leave my ass. How do I love him if I can't even remember what he looks like?

